1
00:00:42,292 --> 00:00:44,961
HIERARCHY

2
00:00:51,384 --> 00:00:52,594
Kenapa kau lakukan itu?

3
00:00:53,678 --> 00:00:54,637
Aku bisa mengurusnya.

4
00:00:55,805 --> 00:00:58,516
Ini akan membuatmu dibicarakan karenaku.

5
00:00:59,976 --> 00:01:01,019
Kang Ha.

6
00:01:06,441 --> 00:01:08,068
Apa tujuanmu di sini?

7
00:01:16,910 --> 00:01:19,162
Jadi, kau sudah tahu siapa aku?

8
00:01:35,595 --> 00:01:37,305
Aku punya misi ke Jooshin.

9
00:01:41,935 --> 00:01:44,395
Benar. Aku akan merebut posisimu, Jae-i.

10
00:01:47,732 --> 00:01:49,400
Peringkat satu sampai lulus.

11
00:01:49,984 --> 00:01:53,071
Jika kupertahankan,
Jooshin akan berikan semuanya.

12
00:01:53,071 --> 00:01:56,241
Biaya hidup, kuliah,
dan daftar kerja di luar negeri.

13
00:01:57,242 --> 00:01:59,202
Kau selalu juara kelas, 'kan?

14
00:01:59,744 --> 00:02:02,831
Murid beasiswa tak pernah
terima keuntungan itu.

15
00:02:04,415 --> 00:02:05,708
Itu akan kudapatkan.

16
00:02:06,292 --> 00:02:08,419
Bersiaplah. Ini tak akan mudah.

17
00:02:08,419 --> 00:02:10,547
Mungkin bagimu itu hanya nilai,

18
00:02:11,422 --> 00:02:14,008
tetapi bagiku ini adalah kesempatan

19
00:02:15,969 --> 00:02:16,803
demi hidupku.

20
00:02:37,574 --> 00:02:39,701
<i>Kenapa kau lakukan itu di depanku?</i>

21
00:02:39,701 --> 00:02:40,660
<i>Ciuman itu?</i>

22
00:02:40,660 --> 00:02:44,372
<i>"Ayo putus." "Kita berteman saja."
Itu sudah jelas.</i>

23
00:02:44,372 --> 00:02:47,834
<i>Jadi, siapa pun yang aku suka,
tak ada urusannya denganmu.</i>

24
00:03:19,157 --> 00:03:21,784
TIDAK ADA HUBUNGAN SAUDARA KANDUNG

25
00:03:30,001 --> 00:03:31,377
<i>Apa tujuanmu di sini?</i>

26
00:03:32,045 --> 00:03:34,547
Jadi, kau sudah tahu siapa aku?

27
00:03:37,425 --> 00:03:38,259
Kang In-han.

28
00:03:40,762 --> 00:03:41,596
Kang Ha.

29
00:04:13,544 --> 00:04:14,420
Mau pergi bersama?

30
00:04:14,420 --> 00:04:18,132
Karena sudah dimulai,
ayo kita lakukan dengan benar.

31
00:04:18,132 --> 00:04:20,260
<i>Kita bisa pergi sekolah bersama</i>

32
00:04:20,260 --> 00:04:22,220
dan tunjukkan secara resmi.

33
00:04:26,224 --> 00:04:27,267
Tidak setuju?

34
00:04:28,601 --> 00:04:30,353
<i>- Jika tak mau...</i>
- Turun jika kutelepon.

35
00:04:39,070 --> 00:04:40,321
Aku pergi, ya.

36
00:05:05,305 --> 00:05:09,309
EPISODE 3
HIERARKI: BEDA LEVEL

37
00:05:17,317 --> 00:05:18,192
Jae-i?

38
00:05:21,321 --> 00:05:22,155
Kenapa diam?

39
00:05:22,780 --> 00:05:24,324
Ayo cepat naik.

40
00:05:32,540 --> 00:05:34,584
Tak usah dilihat. Tak akan jatuh.

41
00:05:36,377 --> 00:05:37,920
Aku tidak takut itu jatuh.

42
00:05:38,629 --> 00:05:39,464
Lantas?

43
00:05:40,548 --> 00:05:41,382
Itu lucu.

44
00:05:42,884 --> 00:05:44,886
Melihat sepedaku di mobil ini.

45
00:05:51,642 --> 00:05:54,145
Norak sekali. Kenapa pakai gelang itu?

46
00:05:55,146 --> 00:05:56,272
Maksudmu ini?

47
00:05:56,272 --> 00:05:58,024
Ini gelang anggota Seonyul.

48
00:05:58,983 --> 00:06:00,777
- "Seonyul"?
- Tim musik.

49
00:06:00,777 --> 00:06:03,529
Pertama kita bertemu,
aku main piano di rumahmu.

50
00:06:03,529 --> 00:06:05,615
Yang main di sana adalah timku.

51
00:06:06,366 --> 00:06:09,077
Semua anggotanya punya gelang yang sama?

52
00:06:09,077 --> 00:06:09,994
Ya.

53
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:11,954
Apa ini norak?

54
00:06:13,373 --> 00:06:14,791
Menurutku ini bagus.

55
00:06:31,224 --> 00:06:33,351
- Jae-i.
- Apa-apaan itu?

56
00:06:34,477 --> 00:06:35,395
Ada apa mereka?

57
00:06:36,938 --> 00:06:39,107
- Apa-apaan dia?
- Lihat tasnya.

58
00:06:39,107 --> 00:06:40,024
Ada apa?

59
00:06:40,525 --> 00:06:42,360
Ayo masuk. Kita bisa terlambat.

60
00:06:43,194 --> 00:06:45,571
- Apa-apaan ini?
- Jangan difoto.

61
00:06:45,571 --> 00:06:46,489
Ri-an...

62
00:06:46,489 --> 00:06:48,199
- Berpegangan.
- Ini serius?

63
00:06:48,199 --> 00:06:50,076
- Mengagumkan.
- Sungguhan?

64
00:06:50,076 --> 00:06:52,578
Hebat. Jae-i dan Kang Ha pegangan tangan.

65
00:06:52,578 --> 00:06:54,497
- Mereka pacaran?
- Benar, 'kan?

66
00:06:54,497 --> 00:06:56,457
- Apa itu?
- Lihat Jae-i.

67
00:06:56,457 --> 00:06:59,210
- Mereka datang ke sekolah begitu?
- Tunggu.

68
00:06:59,210 --> 00:07:00,378
- Jadian?
- Hebat.

69
00:07:00,378 --> 00:07:01,462
Apa ini?

70
00:07:03,881 --> 00:07:06,092
Sungguh luar biasa. Berita besar.

71
00:07:06,092 --> 00:07:07,009
Ambil fotonya.

72
00:07:10,638 --> 00:07:11,681
Ada apa?

73
00:07:11,681 --> 00:07:13,015
Apakah ada masalah?

74
00:07:13,808 --> 00:07:16,352
Tidak. Mana mungkin ada masalah.

75
00:07:28,489 --> 00:07:29,949
Baru kali ini aku lihat.

76
00:07:29,949 --> 00:07:32,660
Jae-i berpegangan tangan
selain dengan Ri-an.

77
00:07:34,203 --> 00:07:37,206
Siapa sebenarnya anak itu? Kang Ha.

78
00:07:38,708 --> 00:07:40,293
Bu Han tak masuk kelas?

79
00:07:43,171 --> 00:07:44,005
Baik, Bu.

80
00:07:46,048 --> 00:07:47,925
Kini mereka terang-terangan?

81
00:07:49,927 --> 00:07:50,761
Lihat fotonya?

82
00:07:51,762 --> 00:07:53,347
Apakah mereka serius?

83
00:07:53,347 --> 00:07:55,600
Hei, jangan ikut membuat keributan.

84
00:07:56,434 --> 00:07:58,019
Semua orang heboh.

85
00:07:58,019 --> 00:08:01,939
Seharusnya kita berikan selamat
dan mendukung pilihan Jae-i, 'kan?

86
00:08:01,939 --> 00:08:04,066
Gila! Ternyata dia serius?

87
00:08:04,066 --> 00:08:06,944
Lantas, bagaimana
dengan Tiran Jooshin, Ri-an?

88
00:08:06,944 --> 00:08:09,363
- Hubungan mereka berakhir?
- Pastinya.

89
00:08:09,363 --> 00:08:11,741
Karena itu dia mulai hubungan baru.

90
00:08:12,742 --> 00:08:13,659
Kalian tahu?

91
00:08:14,243 --> 00:08:16,787
Ri-an juga telah menemukan wanita baru.

92
00:08:17,788 --> 00:08:18,748
Hei.

93
00:08:32,887 --> 00:08:33,930
Apa ini?

94
00:08:33,930 --> 00:08:35,139
Cokelat.

95
00:08:36,057 --> 00:08:36,891
Itu untukmu.

96
00:08:50,196 --> 00:08:51,280
Untuk kalian saja.

97
00:08:51,280 --> 00:08:53,616
Pagi ini aku ada kelas spesial. Dah!

98
00:08:56,869 --> 00:08:58,621
Aku kasihan pada Kim Seon-u.

99
00:08:59,205 --> 00:09:02,208
He-ra tak pernah meliriknya,
tetapi dia terus usaha.

100
00:09:02,208 --> 00:09:03,125
Kau benar.

101
00:09:06,003 --> 00:09:09,131
Itu sejak ulang tahun Woo-jin.
Setelah tidur dengan He-ra.

102
00:09:09,131 --> 00:09:10,216
Hei!

103
00:09:10,800 --> 00:09:12,760
Diamlah. Nanti ada yang dengar.

104
00:09:12,760 --> 00:09:14,845
Lagi pula semua sudah tahu.

105
00:09:14,845 --> 00:09:17,139
Meski begitu, jangan menggosipkannya.

106
00:09:17,139 --> 00:09:19,976
Jangan sampai He-ra dengar.
Kau bisa habis.

107
00:09:21,769 --> 00:09:22,687
Kenapa aku?

108
00:09:22,687 --> 00:09:24,105
SMA JOOSHIN

109
00:09:24,105 --> 00:09:25,648
RUANG PENGAJARAN SPESIAL

110
00:09:31,404 --> 00:09:32,572
Hai, teman-teman.

111
00:09:37,618 --> 00:09:38,911
Itu kursi Jae-i.

112
00:09:39,579 --> 00:09:40,746
Aku yang mengalah.

113
00:09:40,746 --> 00:09:44,041
Memangnya kau bisa fokus
jika duduk di sebelah Jae-i?

114
00:09:52,008 --> 00:09:53,968
- Itu untuk apa?
- Oh, ini...

115
00:09:53,968 --> 00:09:55,052
Itu tempat kami.

116
00:10:01,726 --> 00:10:04,020
Aku ikut kelas ini bersama Jae-i.

117
00:10:04,604 --> 00:10:05,771
Mohon bantuannya.

118
00:10:05,771 --> 00:10:08,524
Apa? Kau tahu ini kelas apa?

119
00:10:08,524 --> 00:10:12,403
Ini hanya untuk kami berempat.
Bukan untuk sembarang orang.

120
00:10:12,403 --> 00:10:13,571
"Sembarang orang"?

121
00:10:15,323 --> 00:10:16,282
He-ra.

122
00:10:24,457 --> 00:10:26,417
Biaya dan jadwalnya sudah diatur.

123
00:10:27,335 --> 00:10:30,546
Jika keberatan ada kami,
aku akan minta kelas terpisah.

124
00:10:33,883 --> 00:10:35,051
Selamat siang.

125
00:10:44,185 --> 00:10:46,312
Kelasnya tidak dimulai?

126
00:10:47,313 --> 00:10:48,147
Baiklah.

127
00:10:49,732 --> 00:10:53,694
Hari ini kita akan melihat
literatur dari abad ke-20.

128
00:10:54,195 --> 00:10:57,907
Ada yang tahu penyair terkenal di era ini?

129
00:11:14,715 --> 00:11:16,509
Kau sungguh akan diam saja?

130
00:11:16,509 --> 00:11:18,469
Dia membawanya ke kelas kita!

131
00:11:20,179 --> 00:11:21,389
Kau harus bertindak.

132
00:11:22,556 --> 00:11:25,559
Ayo beri tahu Jae-i kalau kita berpacaran.

133
00:11:25,559 --> 00:11:27,520
Kau harus menyulutnya agar dia...

134
00:11:29,939 --> 00:11:30,898
Hei, Kim Ri-an!

135
00:11:35,736 --> 00:11:37,697
Jangan berlebihan, Yoon He-ra.

136
00:11:51,043 --> 00:11:54,004
Dia yang membuatku kesal.
Kenapa dia yang marah?

137
00:11:55,715 --> 00:11:57,800
Hei, itu Kang Ha. Luar biasa.

138
00:11:58,592 --> 00:11:59,593
- Hai.
- Hai.

139
00:11:59,593 --> 00:12:00,636
Dia orangnya?

140
00:12:02,263 --> 00:12:04,890
Dia Kang Ha, murid beasiswa.
Namanya Kang Ha.

141
00:12:05,474 --> 00:12:06,475
- Kang Ha?
- Ya.

142
00:12:08,018 --> 00:12:08,853
Hei, Kang Ha.

143
00:12:12,398 --> 00:12:13,399
Ayo kita bicara.

144
00:12:16,026 --> 00:12:18,112
Cepatlah. Ada urusan apa?

145
00:12:20,573 --> 00:12:21,449
Itu...

146
00:12:23,117 --> 00:12:24,410
Maafkan aku.

147
00:12:26,829 --> 00:12:28,622
Aku tak bermaksud begitu.

148
00:12:29,123 --> 00:12:30,249
Kau sedang apa?

149
00:12:30,249 --> 00:12:32,543
Kang Ha, kau tahu posisiku.

150
00:12:32,543 --> 00:12:35,004
Semua tindakan
yang terpaksa kulakukan...

151
00:12:35,504 --> 00:12:37,548
Aku menyesal. Maafkan aku.

152
00:12:39,800 --> 00:12:40,926
Kenapa?

153
00:12:41,635 --> 00:12:42,470
Karena Jae-i?

154
00:12:47,516 --> 00:12:51,103
Waktu itu maupun sekarang,
aku masih tetap murid beasiswa.

155
00:12:51,687 --> 00:12:53,981
Ini konyol sekali, Chan-min.

156
00:12:53,981 --> 00:12:55,941
Ayahku bekerja di Jaeyul Group.

157
00:12:58,986 --> 00:13:00,529
Kau mau menghajarku?

158
00:13:01,697 --> 00:13:03,032
Ayo pukul saja aku.

159
00:13:03,032 --> 00:13:04,867
Aku akan begini...

160
00:13:05,868 --> 00:13:08,788
Aku akan diam begini. Ayo injak aku.

161
00:13:08,788 --> 00:13:09,914
Ayo lakukan.

162
00:13:10,873 --> 00:13:13,459
Kenapa? Kau butuh tongkat?

163
00:13:14,043 --> 00:13:14,877
Akan kuambil.

164
00:13:17,004 --> 00:13:17,838
Pakai ini.

165
00:13:20,299 --> 00:13:22,426
Pukul aku pakai ini sampai patah.

166
00:13:22,426 --> 00:13:26,013
Asalkan jangan bicara
hal buruk tentangku pada Jae-i.

167
00:13:27,181 --> 00:13:29,683
Sepertinya tak ada orang bernyali di sini.

168
00:13:30,559 --> 00:13:34,230
Tentu saja. Jika kau bernyali,
kau tak akan mau merundung orang

169
00:13:34,230 --> 00:13:36,690
hanya karena disuruh anteknya Ri-an.

170
00:13:36,690 --> 00:13:37,608
Benar?

171
00:13:53,457 --> 00:13:55,668
Sial. Semuanya menjadi runyam.

172
00:14:03,801 --> 00:14:06,929
Jadi, Jae-i dan Ri-an
sudah benar-benar putus?

173
00:14:06,929 --> 00:14:08,597
Itu keputusan Jae-i.

174
00:14:09,181 --> 00:14:11,517
Dan kurasa, tidak bagi Ri-an.

175
00:14:12,643 --> 00:14:13,769
Tak disangka.

176
00:14:14,395 --> 00:14:17,273
Kenapa murid beasiswa itu
terlibat dengan Jae-i?

177
00:14:17,273 --> 00:14:18,899
Menurutku, Jae-i sengaja

178
00:14:20,317 --> 00:14:21,151
melakukan itu.

179
00:14:21,861 --> 00:14:23,195
Itu tak akan lama.

180
00:14:23,195 --> 00:14:24,697
Aku khawatir.

181
00:14:25,281 --> 00:14:27,116
Para murid kelihatan gelisah.

182
00:14:28,826 --> 00:14:31,453
Aku takut tragedi itu terjadi lagi.

183
00:14:42,047 --> 00:14:44,258
Apa-apaan kau? Nanti ada yang lihat.

184
00:14:44,258 --> 00:14:45,551
Biar mereka lihat.

185
00:14:46,343 --> 00:14:47,469
Tak akan masalah.

186
00:14:47,469 --> 00:14:50,180
Jangan terlalu khawatir, Bu Han.

187
00:14:55,603 --> 00:14:56,437
Aku pergi, ya.

188
00:15:12,536 --> 00:15:16,457
JANGAN MENANTANG KIM RI-AN. DIA BAHAYA.
BEGITU AWAL KASUS IN-HAN.

189
00:15:57,498 --> 00:15:58,457
Itu punyaku.

190
00:16:35,869 --> 00:16:36,829
Oper padaku.

191
00:17:02,021 --> 00:17:03,564
Ini sangat menjengkelkan.

192
00:17:05,649 --> 00:17:08,235
Tatapannya tenang,
seolah tak ada masalah.

193
00:17:14,533 --> 00:17:16,618
<i>Hanya kau yang bisa melakukannya.</i>

194
00:17:17,119 --> 00:17:18,662
<i>Yang menaruh pesan di lokerku</i>

195
00:17:19,496 --> 00:17:20,748
<i>itu kau, bukan?</i>

196
00:17:25,044 --> 00:17:27,004
AYO KITA BERTEMU

197
00:17:34,553 --> 00:17:35,596
Hai.

198
00:17:35,596 --> 00:17:36,847
Apa rahasiamu?

199
00:17:37,514 --> 00:17:39,725
- Apa?
- Cara bisa akrab dengan Jae-i.

200
00:17:40,225 --> 00:17:42,144
Kau harapan bagi murid beasiswa.

201
00:17:42,728 --> 00:17:45,355
Apa rahasiamu bisa pacaran
dengan Ratu Jae-i?

202
00:17:45,355 --> 00:17:48,150
Boleh aku minta nomormu?

203
00:17:58,911 --> 00:18:00,496
Oke. Ayo fokus!

204
00:18:00,496 --> 00:18:01,997
Jooshin, semangat!

205
00:18:04,333 --> 00:18:05,626
Semangat!

206
00:18:05,626 --> 00:18:07,544
- Ri-an!
- Yun-seok, semangat!

207
00:18:11,673 --> 00:18:13,342
Biru 15!

208
00:18:15,636 --> 00:18:16,637
Bersedia.

209
00:18:18,806 --> 00:18:19,640
Siap.

210
00:18:20,641 --> 00:18:21,892
Mulai. Lempar!

211
00:19:06,353 --> 00:19:07,479
<i>Touchdown!</i>

212
00:19:08,647 --> 00:19:10,607
Aku yang menghalaunya!

213
00:19:10,607 --> 00:19:12,151
- Kau hebat.
- Bagus!

214
00:19:14,278 --> 00:19:15,112
Ri-an hebat!

215
00:19:15,112 --> 00:19:20,242
Kim Ri-an!

216
00:19:22,035 --> 00:19:23,370
Kerennya, Kim Ri-an!

217
00:19:25,914 --> 00:19:26,748
Apa itu?

218
00:19:32,880 --> 00:19:33,964
Mana Jae-i?

219
00:20:02,117 --> 00:20:03,994
<i>Sangat menggemparkan.</i>

220
00:20:03,994 --> 00:20:06,997
Itu perayaan gol yang fantastis.

221
00:20:06,997 --> 00:20:08,916
Kau benar. Dia pria sejati.

222
00:20:09,499 --> 00:20:11,752
Tiran Jooshin sangat romantis.

223
00:20:12,836 --> 00:20:14,796
Bahkan membuat jantungku meledak.

224
00:20:15,923 --> 00:20:19,968
Benar! Kau sempat bilang kalau Ri-an
mungkin saja punya wanita baru.

225
00:20:20,761 --> 00:20:23,222
Jadi, ternyata itu kau.

226
00:20:23,222 --> 00:20:26,850
Ya, bohong jika aku bilang
tak ada tanda-tanda akan begini.

227
00:20:27,392 --> 00:20:29,061
Aku sudah punya firasat.

228
00:20:29,061 --> 00:20:32,564
Bisa-bisanya tak cerita pada kami.
Aku kecewa, Ratu He-ra.

229
00:20:34,900 --> 00:20:37,277
- Ratu He-ra?
- Kau mencapai status itu.

230
00:20:37,277 --> 00:20:40,072
Kau pacar baru Ri-an
yang dicium di depan umum.

231
00:20:41,406 --> 00:20:42,241
Ada-ada saja.

232
00:20:47,579 --> 00:20:49,456
Astaga. Kim Seon-u lagi.

233
00:20:50,040 --> 00:20:51,250
Mengesankan.

234
00:20:52,292 --> 00:20:54,002
Naiklah. Aku mau bicara.

235
00:20:55,003 --> 00:20:56,004
Kalian pulanglah.

236
00:21:06,431 --> 00:21:09,393
Apakah Seon-u begitu karena dia syok?

237
00:21:10,143 --> 00:21:12,437
- Karena Ri-an mencium He-ra?
- Ya.

238
00:21:13,355 --> 00:21:16,358
Mereka ke mana?
