290
00:25:33,907 --> 00:25:35,242
Ayo kita pergi!

291
00:25:35,909 --> 00:25:37,452
Kita mengobrol sambil makan.

292
00:25:39,871 --> 00:25:42,457
Dasar gila. Beraninya menyentuhku!

293
00:25:44,251 --> 00:25:45,085
Hei, Tae-ho.

294
00:25:49,631 --> 00:25:51,258
<i>Putra tunggal Hotel Jaeyul.</i>

295
00:25:51,841 --> 00:25:53,134
Mereka hanya tahu itu.

296
00:25:53,969 --> 00:25:56,054
Tak ada yang tahu latar belakangku.

297
00:25:57,097 --> 00:25:58,348
Jadi, aku menghindari

298
00:25:59,391 --> 00:26:00,225
In-han...

299
00:26:02,227 --> 00:26:03,061
dan juga kau.

300
00:26:03,687 --> 00:26:04,896
Aku paham posisimu.

301
00:26:05,689 --> 00:26:07,816
Meski begitu, kau mau membantuku.

302
00:26:11,611 --> 00:26:14,364
Aku tahu kau juga
berikan kertas pada kakakku.

303
00:26:15,407 --> 00:26:16,449
Kenapa masuk Jooshin?

304
00:26:17,701 --> 00:26:19,327
Ada apa dengan Jae-i?

305
00:26:20,579 --> 00:26:21,997
Jangan bertindak bahaya.

306
00:26:21,997 --> 00:26:26,376
Aku tak tahu apa maksud Jae-i,
tetapi dia dan Ri-an sudah lama bersama.

307
00:26:26,376 --> 00:26:27,294
Aku tahu.

308
00:26:28,628 --> 00:26:30,547
Karena itu aku ingin ada di sisinya.

309
00:26:31,047 --> 00:26:33,466
Ternyata kau sengaja mengusiknya.

310
00:26:34,342 --> 00:26:35,343
Kim Ri-an.

311
00:26:37,929 --> 00:26:39,723
In-han sempat meneleponku.

312
00:26:41,808 --> 00:26:43,893
Jelas terjadi sesuatu padanya.

313
00:26:45,270 --> 00:26:48,773
Namun, polisi tak tahu
apa yang terjadi dan siapa pelakunya.

314
00:26:51,026 --> 00:26:52,110
Dianggap tabrak lari.

315
00:26:52,110 --> 00:26:55,322
Polisi bahkan tak tahu.
Lantas kau mau melakukan apa?

316
00:26:55,322 --> 00:26:56,573
Kumpulkan bukti.

317
00:26:57,198 --> 00:26:59,200
Miras, narkoba, penindasan...

318
00:26:59,784 --> 00:27:02,495
Kim Ri-an, yang melakukan itu pada kakaku.

319
00:27:03,038 --> 00:27:05,415
Akan kuungkap semua kasus
di SMA Jooshin.

320
00:27:06,958 --> 00:27:09,252
Karena itu, tolong bantu aku.

321
00:27:11,046 --> 00:27:12,339
Aku bisa apa?

322
00:27:12,339 --> 00:27:15,091
Aku butuh sandi loker Kim Ri-an.

323
00:27:16,092 --> 00:27:17,302
Sandi?

324
00:27:17,302 --> 00:27:19,721
Yun-seok memasok narkoba padanya.

325
00:27:19,721 --> 00:27:21,598
Pasti ada bukti di sana.

326
00:27:22,557 --> 00:27:25,602
Aku sulit mendekati mereka,
tetapi tidak bagimu.

327
00:27:27,562 --> 00:27:28,605
Itu masuk akal.

328
00:27:28,605 --> 00:27:31,232
Akan tetapi, aku juga

329
00:27:32,275 --> 00:27:33,109
agak takut.

330
00:27:34,152 --> 00:27:35,070
Aku mohon.

331
00:27:36,488 --> 00:27:37,530
Tae-ho.

332
00:28:43,304 --> 00:28:44,139
Bicaralah.

333
00:28:45,140 --> 00:28:46,599
Itu tujuanmu ke sini, 'kan?

334
00:28:48,101 --> 00:28:50,979
Apa niatmu, sampai melibatkan He-ra?

335
00:28:55,024 --> 00:28:58,570
Setahuku, kini di antara kita
tak lagi harus menjelaskan

336
00:28:59,070 --> 00:29:02,490
setiap detail dengan siapa
dan apa saja yang aku lakukan.

337
00:29:03,783 --> 00:29:04,701
Kim Ri-an.

338
00:29:04,701 --> 00:29:05,910
YOON HE-RA

339
00:29:13,710 --> 00:29:16,421
<i>Sudah sampai rumah? Aku mau mengobrol.</i>

340
00:29:17,046 --> 00:29:18,506
<i>Kau sedang senggang?</i>

341
00:29:18,506 --> 00:29:19,674
Datang ke rumahku.

342
00:29:20,967 --> 00:29:21,801
Mengobrol di sini.

343
00:29:37,233 --> 00:29:39,402
<i>Ke rumah Ri-an? Semalam ini?</i>

344
00:29:39,402 --> 00:29:42,322
Tadi aku meneleponnya
karena mau mengobrol.

345
00:29:43,573 --> 00:29:45,074
Dia malah mengundangku.

346
00:29:45,575 --> 00:29:48,912
Gila. Bukankah langkah kalian
terlalu cepat?

347
00:29:49,829 --> 00:29:51,080
Bagaimana penampilanku?

348
00:29:51,790 --> 00:29:53,833
Kelihatannya wajahku agak bengkak.

349
00:29:54,793 --> 00:29:56,878
Sangat cantik. Seperti dewi!

350
00:29:56,878 --> 00:29:57,796
<i>Kau cantik!</i>

351
00:29:57,796 --> 00:29:58,880
- Benarkah?
<i>- Ya.</i>

352
00:29:58,880 --> 00:30:00,965
Hei, bukankah dia cantik?

353
00:30:00,965 --> 00:30:02,842
<i>He-ra sangat cantik.</i>

354
00:30:04,052 --> 00:30:06,095
<i>Hebat sekali. Kau cerdas.</i>

355
00:30:06,095 --> 00:30:07,597
Nanti kutelepon lagi.

356
00:30:26,574 --> 00:30:27,992
Cepat sekali kau sampai.

357
00:30:30,161 --> 00:30:30,995
Hei, Jae-i.

358
00:30:34,457 --> 00:30:37,377
Tadi tiba-tiba Ri-an
menyuruhku ke rumahnya.

359
00:30:37,877 --> 00:30:39,087
Ada yang mau kubicarakan.

360
00:30:40,046 --> 00:30:42,048
Aku mau bahas tentang hari ini.

361
00:30:42,048 --> 00:30:45,844
Meski hubungan kalian memburuk,
aku tetap saja kaget.

362
00:30:46,594 --> 00:30:48,721
Terlebih, kita adalah sahabat.

363
00:30:49,806 --> 00:30:52,308
Tenang saja. Aku akan bicarakan dengannya.

364
00:30:54,394 --> 00:30:57,313
Jangan mengikuti permainan konyol Ri-an.

365
00:31:08,491 --> 00:31:09,617
"Permainan konyol"?

366
00:31:39,606 --> 00:31:40,648
Lama tak berkunjung.

367
00:31:41,816 --> 00:31:42,650
Kau benar.

368
00:31:43,234 --> 00:31:45,528
Kulihat lobinya makin bagus.

369
00:31:46,112 --> 00:31:47,280
Mari saya antar.

370
00:32:33,034 --> 00:32:34,410
<i>Dia mau kau bunuh juga?</i>

371
00:32:45,630 --> 00:32:46,881
<i>Kau yakin dengan ini?</i>

372
00:32:47,382 --> 00:32:48,216
<i>Aku yakin.</i>

373
00:32:50,051 --> 00:32:52,303
<i>Aku terus mengeceknya berkali-kali.</i>

374
00:32:53,888 --> 00:32:57,183
<i>Jika dia tahu, aku akan diasingkan
seperti ibuku.</i>

375
00:33:00,019 --> 00:33:02,689
<i>Ini bukan sekadar ancaman.
Aku punya semuanya.</i>

376
00:33:03,272 --> 00:33:04,691
<i>Ini dan juga itu.</i>

377
00:33:05,400 --> 00:33:06,776
<i>Apa maumu?</i>

378
00:33:10,363 --> 00:33:11,197
DIBACA

379
00:33:22,125 --> 00:33:22,959
Ada apa?

380
00:33:26,087 --> 00:33:27,088
Ayah mencarimu.

381
00:33:33,261 --> 00:33:35,013
Sudah menentukan gaunmu?

382
00:33:35,013 --> 00:33:36,681
Untuk Malam Orang Tua?

383
00:33:36,681 --> 00:33:39,308
