476
00:41:26,942 --> 00:41:28,986
Tak berlaku untuk murid beasiswa.

477
00:41:29,487 --> 00:41:30,446
Tak berlaku?

478
00:41:32,323 --> 00:41:35,910
Kami dilarang hadir.
