479
00:41:35,910 --> 00:41:37,786
Anak keluarga kaya datang,

480
00:41:37,786 --> 00:41:40,623
murid beasiswa dilarang?
Sekolah macam apa itu?

481
00:41:41,499 --> 00:41:42,500
Justru itu bagus.

482
00:41:42,500 --> 00:41:45,461
Tak perlu ke acara formal,
dan bisa dapat gaji.

483
00:41:46,086 --> 00:41:47,379
Itu bagus.

484
00:41:48,047 --> 00:41:49,173
Dasimu miring lagi.

485
00:41:49,715 --> 00:41:52,092
Padahal In-han selalu teliti dan rapi.

486
00:41:54,345 --> 00:41:55,179
Kau ini!

487
00:41:55,846 --> 00:41:58,974
Itu semua karenanya.
